msgid "Collaborating and Contributing in Open Science"
msgstr ""

#: ../../scipy-conference/manual/committees/bofs.rst:275
msgid "As evidenced by SciPy 2013, there are many great open science projects. The Center for Open Science and the infrastructure being developed (the Open Science Framework) seeks to connect these projects and support collaboration. We will discuss collaboration possibilities, how developers might get involved, and how best to encourage community contribution to these efforts."
