#: ../../scipy-conference/manual/mailings/tutorials_welcome_tutors.rst:14
msgid "All installation steps need to be done well *BEFORE* the tutorial to ensure success. Tutor need to post detailed installation instructions at least *2 weeks* before as well as an installation testing script. We will contact the students informing them that they need to make sure they are setup for the tutorial before the tutorial start as no installation time will be scheduled during the tutorial. They will be encouraged to visit the tutorial page to find your material and come to the class with their computer already setup."
