#: ../../scipy-conference/manual/program/reviewer_guidelines.rst:70
msgid "Pay attention to your projections about the work being evaluated."
msgstr ""

#: ../../scipy-conference/manual/program/reviewer_guidelines.rst:72
msgid "Look for patterns of assessment among different groups. For example, are women in general rated differently than men?"
