#: ../../scipy-conference/manual/program/reviewer_guidelines.rst:74
msgid "Look out for Semantic gender priming: exposure to words more strongly associated with male (e.g., aggressive, competitive) or female (e.g., supportive, nurturing) stereotypes affects subsequent evaluation of male or female targets. |ref_7|_"
